window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Good girl Quinn didn’t expect her night to turn to mayhem once she stepped into a legendary Halloween party. After needing a quick rescue from a stranger, she finds herself locked in a captivating game of infatuation with three masked men. Her one demand? The game ends at dawn.</p> <p>As desire collides with danger, how much can Quinn take before the sun comes up? Will her condition of only one night be enough? Or will her masked men leave their mark?</p> <p>DISCLAIMER:</p> <p>If you’re looking for a story with a solid plot, then this is not the book for you. If you’re looking for a short, spicy Halloween read with masked men to fulfill your darkest fantasies, then this is meant for you. Listening to this novella is not required in order to read the rest of the series. For character backstories and plot you may skip and proceed to Bloodshed.</p> <p>Scream For Us contains mature and graphic content that is not suitable for all audiences. This is a Dark Romance/Thriler/Horror, Why Choose Novella. Please check trigger warnings at the beginning of the book before proceeding.</p>"; 
